9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1274, L.D. 1913, “An Act to Allow
10 Matinicus Isle Plantation to Issue a Revenue Bond for Urgently Needed Repairs to the
11 Plantation's Electric Power Generating Facility”
12 Amend the bill by inserting before section 1 the following:
13 'Sec. 1. P&SL 1975, c. 25, §4 is amended to read:
14 Sec. 4. The plantation is also authorized to issue general obligation bonds, not to
15 exceed the general law, to pay the cost of the acquisition, construction, reconsrtuction
16 reconstruction, improvement, extension and enlargement of, and equipment for, the electric
17 power generating facility. Schedules for the payment of the principal and interest on the
18 bonds shall be established in conformance with the rules and regulations of the Public
19 Utilities Commission.'
20 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
21 number to read consecutively.
22 SUMMARY
2233 This amendment removes the requirement that schedules for the payment of the
2244 principal and interest on general obligation bonds issued by Matinicus Isle Plantation must
2255 be established in conformity with rules and regulations of the Public Utilities Commission
2266 and makes a technical correction.
